content:
Paruresis:
Paruresis is considered to be a social phobia. In general, if you live with paruresis, you fear negative evaluation by others related to using public toilets. If this fear is severe and limits your life, it may be diagnosed as social anxiety disorder

My diagnosis
• I took the RCADS (revised child’s anxiety and depression scale)
• I was diagnosed with social phobia, panic disorder, major depression and mild OCD. 
• This was a shock but now i get the help i need 💘
